          "id": "f2",
          "description": "<completion> frozen state uses 'no material pushback remains' but <inputs> governance config uses freeze_requires_no_material_pushback without defining 'material' — inferable from context (blocking+major) but never stated explicitly",
          "source_section": "<completion> and <inputs>"
        }
      ],
      "redesign_guidance": "Add one canonical definition of 'material pushback' (blocking or major severity) in <guardrails> and use that single phrasing consistently in <role>, <guardrails>, and <completion>."
